text: I'm heading home now for maximum winter driver avoidance. Will be back online and working when I get there til party time!

<!channel> As a reminder to everyone, we’re still in crunch mode on compass working towards feature complete, and need to send out solid iOS and Android builds today. Please take advantage of working from home if you are and keep heads down and push forward. We’ll all be available via slack as questions arise, so keep on keepin on. Hoping to see those JIRA tickets fly by. Thanks everyone.
